            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>中国疾控中心专家表示，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不少呼吸道感染性疾病可通过疫苗预防#</span></a>】近期呼吸道疾病的高发，给多地的医疗机构带来了不小的压力，中国疾控中心专家表示，目前，不少呼吸道感染性疾病可以通过打疫苗来有效预防。对于重点人群，早期治疗非常重要👇🏻 （科普中国）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4972627463438372" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">小央视频的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/006WAXimly8hk9fhkwmb9j30zk0k0gp7.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/4Qvws660lx08auH7jvFm01041200rWBn0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701105416&amp;ssig=%2BtmrPOATYp&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dtK4b4D8lx08auH6UGgw01041200exnD0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701105416&amp;ssig=Z0NcOs2BPX&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/H1HUSHnglx08auH6KjVu0104120095iS0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701105416&amp;ssig=0r89S%2FIhKf&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.c